item.title: CVE-2019-11826|2024-09-16T16:43:02.971Z -- synology -- photo%20moments
item.description: Relative path traversal vulnerability in SYNO.PhotoTeam.Upload.Item in Synology Moments before 1.3.0-0691 allows remote authenticated users to upload arbitrary files via the name parameter.
